  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 3. Full 13-factor review: 10 factors assessed (all meeting required levels), 3 factors carried as not-assessed on the basis that they were considered beyond the scope of the current submission cycle.",
